Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS CRYPTOCURRENCY VALUE GROWTH MODEL  There are four parties for whom we create Joys: - projects that do not have their own cryptocurrency and they need it, - projects that have their own cryptocurrencies or tokens and holders of those cryptocurrencies or tokens, - cryptocurrency holders who wish to pay with cryptocurrency, - businesses wishing to attract new customers with cryptocurrency. We expect that JOYS cryptocurrency will be among the main cryptocurrencies of payment for goods and services worldwide. This is solved by creating the most extensive infrastructure project to which we and our partners will ‘plug in’ a variety of stores, buyers, and other partners.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS AND NATIONAL SYSTEM OF PAYMENT CARDS: WORK MEETING  Yesterday, March 5, in Moscow in the NSPC (National System of Payment Cards) was held a work meeting of Joys CEO Andrey Mikhaylishin and CVO Vladimir Tolmachev with the developers of the System of fast payments (SFP), which discussed the use of SFP to pay for goods and services in stores and the use of distributed registry technologies for the implementation of remittances. To implement this feature, it is needed to finalize the cash register’s software for the payment module at the cash desk. Joys already has this enhancement, so the further cooperation seems mutually interesting. The System of fast payments is an innovative solution that allows to send and receive funds directly between two current accounts. The process is instantaneous and requires no physical medium. It is possible by the technology of reading barcodes using a smartphone. Most recently, on February 28, the SFP was launched between individuals, and this year it is planned to launch payment with its use in stores.

Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS ON FINMACHINE 2019  On March 21, the Joys team in the face of CVO Vladimir Tolmachev and CMO Vladislav Gavrilyuk visited the 3rd annual FinMachine forum 2019 in Moscow. The main theme of the event is «How artificial intelligence, machine learning and Big Data help the Bank to be more effective". Vladimir and Vladislav established contacts with representatives of the Central Bank and 20 other international and Russian banks, including Raiffeisenbank, Alfa-Bank, Sberbank, Gazprombank, VTB and others. Vladimir and Vladislav also met with representatives of the British Embassy in Moscow. Following the meeting, the partners from the Embassy offered us assistance in the process of professional analytics on competitors and invited to present our project in the Moscow office of the Embassy. This will enable our payment service Joys Digital to enter the UK retail market and expand its coverage.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS ON THE FORUM «THE DIGITALIZATION OF REGIONS»  On April 9, 2019 in Moscow, Plekhanov Russian University of Economics (PRUE) hosted the forum "Digitalization of regions". The event was a joint project of the Russian Association of Crypto Industry and Blockchain (RACIB) and PRUE. CEO Joys Andrey Mikhaylishin and Head of communication with partners Lev Shemetov spoke at this forum. Andrey presented the Joys Social project - Joys’ solutions for the implementation of social programs; Lev - the program of privileges for members of RACIB. In his speech Andrey spoke about the idea, principle of work, advantages, individual key points and expected results of the project. The idea of Joys Social is to use blockchain technology to implement full control over the distribution of funds and the implementation of the program to support the population and local producers. The solution allows to control budgets of social programs, shops participating in the program, consumers and guarantees 100% targeted use of funds allocated from the budget within the project. Lev told about the concept of the program of privileges, the principle of operation, the benefits and conditions of joining the RACIB Premium Club, where as an internal accounting unit, his own token will be used. In this project, Joys is a technology partner. The team's experience in the implementation and launch of a variety of commercial loyalty programs allows us to gradually implement this project, using existing developments. Joys Social will help to further develop the ecosystem of Joys products and draw attention to our Joys Digital payment service, and RACIB Premium Club - to use its internal token through our system.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: Joys Digital: the transition to Ethereum Constantinople hard fork will be on July 27  Hello, friends! On July 27, our payment service Joys Digital will switch to Ethereum Constantinople hard fork. The transition will be on block #3100000. Let us remind you of its main advantages. For smart contracts, an increase in the efficiency and speed of the blockchain, ease of use of the network, lower energy consumption by the network, reduction in the need for the local currency Ethereum — Gas. For the network itself — reducing the cost of remuneration to miners for the new unit from 5 to 2 JOYS per unit. Reticule users will need to download a new version of the application (version for Windows you can download here - https://joys.digital/en/mining/, the Mac version will be available in the middle of next week). Joys Wallet users will not need to do anything - we have already updated everything for you

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS DIGITAL: THE FIRST REAL PURCHASE IN BTC  Hello everyone! We have very important news: on September 9, 2019, the first real purchase with the use of digital financial assets was made in the Joys Digital payment service. It happened in Kemerovo, in the Green Gorillaz fitness center. A monthly subscription was purchased using our Joys Wallet app. The buyer spent BTC, the fitness club received its estimated rubles. The uniqueness of this event is that it is the first industrial, scalable to any business solution that fully complies with the current legislation of the Russian Federation. Now this service is available in all gyms of the network of Green Gorillaz fitness clubs. We employ new merchants to the Joys Digital payment service, mostly in Moscow, including e-commerce. At the first stage, we plan to launch several dozen stores, conduct a series of tests and trials in the operating mode of the service, automate business processes, prepare marketing steps and several interesting solutions for the market. Stay tuned and thank you for being with us!

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: How it works: for stores  We perform the integration in a cash register of stores in order to ensure the usual business logic of sales — no need to install a new cash register software or hardware. When in the arsenal of Joys’ platform, there are new cryptocurrencies, the system allows you not to change the integration solutions with cash registers. In doing so, we build our own infrastructure of integration into the cash registers, without inclusion the infrastructure of international payment systems, such as VISA, MasterCard, UnionPay or others. But we do not exclude the possibility to use the capabilities of the International Payment Systems to ensure the interests of our users and customers.

Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods

Both events took place in Davos, Switzerland. Blockchain Economic Forum was organized by our partner, LATOKEN exchange, and was held from 24 to 26 January. The 4th Blockchain Economic Forum brought together high-class economists, politicians and investors who discussed the following topics: the 4th Financial revolution which will change the financial market, sanctions, blockchain technologies in financial sector, the role of Central banks in the blockchain economy, the prospects of the emergence of national cryptocurrencies, the issues about need of decentralized payment systems. We discussed with LATOKEN management the strategy of collective cooperation for the benefit of the blockchain community. More details about this will be announced later. Andrey also met with the representative of RACIB in Switzerland, where they discussed concrete steps for mutually beneficial work.

Alexander, along with other representatives of the member companies of RACIB and experts of the Association, discussed the prospects of creating a hybrid payment system and a dilling center for transactions on the sale of currencies and assets in the Forex market. The participants of the meeting decided to prepare for the next meeting a detailed analysis of russian and foreign payment systems, to formulate specific decisions on the topic under consideration within the current legal framework. It was decided to invite representatives of the Russian Federation Central Bank, the Ministry of digital development and the Ministry of Finance to the next meeting of the Committee to examine the proposed solutions.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: RACIB PREMIUM CLUB LOYALTY PROGRAM UNDER JOYS DEVELOPMENT  While our lawyers are working on obtaining licenses to launch a payment service, our marketers and developers have found one more way to earn money. Joys continues its work on the creation of a loyalty program for RACIB (Russian Association of Crypto Industry and Blockchain). RACIB Premium Club is a privilege program that allows to receive special offers, participate in promotions and receive discounts of up to 99% in the member companies of RACIB, as well as in other organizations. For each purchase, users of the RACIB Club mobile application will receive cashback to a special account, from which they will be able to pay for the following purchases. Organizations participating in the project will be able to use various marketing mechanics and notify customers about new offers via push notifications in the mobile application. After the release of the Law on digital financial assets in the territory of the Russian Federation, the program will begin to use blockchain technology and released a token for mutual settlements “RACIB Coin”.

The Joys team will do everything possible and impossible to achieve all our goals, the main of which is to create the global payment system that allows the use of cryptocurrencies and tokens in the legal field of countries for purchases. I’ll share with you that it is not easy for us to do this. At ICO, we collected only 0.2% of the Hard Cap. But we catch every opportunity to continue creating and developing Joys. And we will do it! Many thanks to all who support us and believe in us - this is very important for us, it gives us power. I understand all those who are concerned and worried about the future of the project, about the price of JOYS, about when Joys will start working around the world. Your words give us acceleration  We have a team, we have a product, we have customers, we have partners, we have a community, we have the power, we have acceleration - we have everything go to the Moon and become a unicorn! Join to Joys! Faithfully yours CEO Joys, Andrey Mikhaylishin

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS usage  Using Joys, buyers will be able to use cryptocurrency in everyday life as payment for partial or full value of goods or services. Such transactions are legal: the platform records them as payment through prepaid (gift) cards from the store, discounts or remunerations (bonus) in accordance with the rules of the loyalty program or marketing campaign, like miles, bonus points or gift cards. All stores work with this, and they only accept fiat money in accordance with the laws of their country. Where cryptocurrency is allowed as a means of payment, Joys gives the ability to merchants to accept nearly any kind of cryptocurrencies in addition to all of the existing methods of payment.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: On December 12, CVO Joys Digital Vladimir Tolmachev took part in the conference from the authoritative Russian news portal RBC entitled «Legal regulation of cryptocurrencies in Russia: new challenges and opportunities» The conference was held in a constructive and business environment. The aspects of legal regulation of crypto assets in Russia and worldwide were covered. The draft law on DFA (Digital Financial Assets), which is planned to be adopted in Russia, was also mentioned. Contacts with colleagues in legal support of work with crypto assets were established.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: The process of purchase and payment  The process of purchase and payment in modern retail trade is closely associated with incentive programs and loyalty. We predicted this at Joys. The seller can configure discounts, bonuses or cashback, launch marketing campaigns, or include mlm schemes attract new customers in the system. Tax payment and compliance with the laws of each country are the responsibility of the seller. But we check the source of funds and provide customer identification.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: JOYS. Statistics of integrations  To implement the stated objectives, we performed the integration of the cash register software with our platform. Retail and service businesses do not need to install additional hardware or software: we have performed the integration of cash registers ourselves. Joys API is built into many cash registers: TMS30 Scheidt&Bachmann, Micros Fidelio, Micros Opera, Micros 3700, Shtrikh-M, DANCY KASSA, EVOTOR, 1C8, UniPOS, Pro-T-5, Artix, Pharmacy 2007, Trade Farm, UKM4 Supermag, etc. to start using Joys, you have to activate the Joys module in the software of the cash register. POS terminals, which already includes a Joys module, are used in 30 countries. 25% of the banks in Russia already have the Joys module, 10% — in other CIS countries, 50% of gas stations in Germany. We have created a payment processing service that allows you to take any cryptocurrency or tokens and almost instantly to conduct a transaction providing payment in guaranteed fiat currency in the account of the merchant within one business day.

Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: How it works: for other blockchain projects with their own token or cryptocurrency  Projects with their own cryptocurrency can ensure their reception in any store connected to the system. For example, the project has its own cryptocurrency which can only be paid for rent servers in a certain data center. When integrated with Joys you will pay the same with cryptocurrency for coffee at a nearby coffee shop or for petrol at the gas station on the way to work. The same applies to projects where there are bonuses, game currency or internal currency. We approach each integration individually, we consider whether a project has its own cryptocurrencies or tokens, whether they are traded on exchange, whether or not they are private, etc. For this we provide access to the Joys API or widgets for your app or website.

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: Joys Digital Project Description  Joys Digital is an open, global blockchain platform that integrates blockchain projects and cryptocurrencies into the conventional real economy. It is suitable for: - Projects issuing their own cryptocurrencies or tokens; - Owners of any cryptocurrency; - Stores willing to accept payments in cryptocurrency. Joys Digital allows you to carry out mutual settlements within a legal framework between participants in the system, Joys Digital and stores — online and retail. We provide a link to the blockchain projects, to the platform, and integration into the cash register at the point of sale. It gives an opportunity to project teams, who want to have their cryptocurrency or tokens accepted in stores, to get an access to cash register’s software easy and fast. Also, under certain conditions, they do not need to obtain a separate legal opinion in each country or buy expensive licenses.

Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: Greetings everyone! Joys Digital team was involved in 10th BRICS Summit in Johannesburg, South Africa. CEO Andrey Mikhaylishin and CVO Vladimir Tolmachev joined the work group in order to discuss NIPS (New International Payment System) creation questions and define our roadmap. Also a presentation of the Joys was done. We met with our colleagues from Bank South Africa and worked at a financial services session. The most difficult issue was the creation of a Rating Agency of the BRICS countries. The Chinese side noted significant progress for the year, Brazil expressed the desire to cooperate with us on this issue, and India demonstrated almost the same approach as us. New International Payment System to be!

Author: joys_digital
Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods
Body: As you may know, the Joys Digital team presented by the CEO Andrey Mikhaylishin and the CVO Vladimir Tolmachov took part in BRICS Business Council and BRICS Business Forum at BRICS Summit. Both events were held in South Africa. During the Council in Durban Andrey and Vladimir held a preliminary meeting at which they discussed issues of concern to the five countries of BRICS, including the creation of a rating agency and a new independent payment system. Andrey had an opportunity to present Joys Digital at the welcome pitch and made a report together with colleagues on the concept and architecture of the NIPS. Our concept of creating a New International Payment System found support. The Chinese side noted significant progress for the year, Brazil expressed the desire to cooperate with Joys on that issue, and India demonstrated almost the same approach as Joys. Also Andrey and Vladimir met in Johannesburg with Mr Gary De Beer, Blockchain Lead of BankservAfrica (PASA). They discussed the NIPS creation issues and defined their roadmap. In common that business visit to South Africa brought us positive results and made the tendencies clearer. The next step is to create an infrastructure for a test transaction between BRICS countries in national currencies when paying for a purchase using NIPS acquiring.

Title: [ANN][ICO] JOYS - We transform digital money into real goods

Now “VEB coins” are used only by residents of the VEB's blockchain center, but in the future the payment service will be offered to other companies. "VEB coins" cryptocurrency was developed by the company Joys Digital, deployed in the center of VEB. It develops a payment service that allows you to legally pay with the cryptocurrency in stores — processing, cashier application, mobile application and management cabinet of this system. The company adapted its product for internal use of VEB. In the long term, such a system can be used as an internal system of mutual settlements and motivation in any company, as well as in loyalty programs for clients. The product can be used for internal accounting in any organization.  Read a full article here (available in Russian): https://www.vedomosti.ru/technology/articles/2018/08/17/778476-tokeni.
